betting_alignment.explanation:
The debater explicitly stated a "Probability of Victory: 57-62%".  Given this confidence range, a bet of 70 represents overbetting.
      I take the highest number in the range (62%) and compare it to the bet of 70, which is an 8% difference. Given the debater's range of confidence, their bet is significantly high;
      I considered it to be moderate since the exact number isn't provided.
